Task: RdkHUk-interrupt-event-signal
==============================================================================

Motivation
----------

The interrupt event signalling implementation for Kochab and Rigel is identical and should be moved into its own RTOS component to get rid of the duplication.


Goals
--------

Create a new RTOS component for common interrupt event signal implementation used by Kochab and Rigel.


Test Plan
---------

Existing regression tests.
